{
  "name": "Interior",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Interior/Interior .htm#Interior.Interior\">Interior</a></strong> 属性可返回 <strong>Interior</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将 Sheet1 中 A1 单元格内部设置为红色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表中 A1:C4 区域单元格的内部添加十字线图案。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:C4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pattern</span> = xlPatternCrissCross\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表一个对象的内部。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个代表 ET 应用程序的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a></strong> 对象。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个代表指定对象的创建程序的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象（可对一个 OLE 自动化对象使用该属性来返回该对象的应用程序）。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> test{\n  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n      <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n  }\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n      <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n  }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Color",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>Border</strong></th>\n<th>边框的颜色。</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>Borders</strong></td>\n<td>一个区域的所有四条边的颜色。如果四边不是同一种颜色，则 <strong>Color</strong> 返回的是 0（零）。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Font</strong></td>\n<td>字体的颜色。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Interior</strong></td>\n<td>单元格底纹的颜色或图形对象的填充颜色。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Tab</strong></td>\n<td>选项卡的颜色。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置对象的主要颜色，如注释部分中的表格所示。使用 <strong>RGB</strong> 函数可创建颜色值。<strong>Variant</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将活动工作表B2单元格背景颜色设置为黄色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将 Sheet1 中 A1:C4 区域单元格背景颜色设置为红色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:C4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ColorIndex",
      "summary": "<p>颜色可指定为当前调色板中颜色的索引值，也可指定为下列 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlColorIndex 枚举.html\">XlColorIndex</a></strong> 常量之一：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>xlColorIndexAutomatic</strong></li>\n<li><strong>xlColorIndexNone</strong></li>\n</ul>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个<strong>Variant</strong> 值，它代表内部颜色。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将 Sheet1 中 C2 单元格内部设置为红色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将活动工作表中 A1:D5 区域单元格内部设置为无颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:D5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = xlColorIndexNone\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示创建对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Gradient",
      "summary": "<p>使用 LinearGradient 或 RectangularGradient。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置所选内容的 <strong>Interior</strong> 对象的 <strong>Gradient</strong> 属性。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将 Sheet1 中 A1:E4 区域单元格内部设置为线性渐变填充，渐变填充角度为45度，然后添加 ColorStop 对象并设置其颜色为绿色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:E4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pattern</span> = xlPatternLinearGradient\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Degree</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">45</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Gradient</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorStops</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表中 A1 单元格内部的线性渐变填充角度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`渐变角度为 <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${interior.Gradient.Degree}</span> 度`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Pattern",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个包含 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlPattern 枚举.html\">xlPattern</a></strong> 常量的 <strong>Variant</strong> 值，它代表内部图案。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在 Sheet1 中 A1 单元格的内部添加十字图案。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pattern</span> = xlPatternCrissCross\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表中 A1:C4 单元格的内部添加网格图案。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:C4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pattern</span> = xlPatternGrid\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "PatternColor",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>以 RGB 值返回或设置内部图案的颜色。可读/写 <strong>Variant</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例对 Sheet1 中 A1:C3 区域单元格添加棋盘图案，并将图案设置为红色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:C3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pattern</span> = xlPatternChecker\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PatternColor</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断活动工作表 A1:C5 区域图案颜色是否为蓝色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:C5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PatternColor</span> == <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "PatternColorIndex",
      "summary": "<p>将本属性设置为 <strong>xlColorIndexAutomatic</strong>，表示单元格使用自动图案或图形对象使用自动填充样式。将本属性设置为 <strong>xlColorIndexNone</strong>，则表示不希望使用图案（等价于将 <strong>Interior</strong> 对象的 <strong>Pattern</strong> 属性设置为 <strong>xlPatternNone</strong>）。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置内部图案的颜色，表示为当前调色板中的颜色编号或下列 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlColorIndex 枚举.html\">XlColorIndex</a></strong> 常量之一：<strong>xlColorIndexAutomatic</strong> 或 <strong>xlColorIndexNone</strong>。<strong>Long</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例对 Sheet1 中 A1:B2 区域单元格添加棋盘图案，并将图案设置为蓝色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:B2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pattern</span> = xlChecker\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PatternColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例对活动工作表中 D4 单元格添加网格图案，并将图案颜色设置为自动配色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pattern</span> = xlPatternGrid\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PatternColorIndex</span> = xlColorIndexAutomatic\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "PatternThemeColor",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置 <strong>Interior</strong> 对象的主题颜色图案。可读/写 <strong>Variant</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例为活动工作表中 A1:B2 区域单元格添加网格图案，并将图案主题颜色设置为 xlThemeColorAccent1。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:B2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pattern</span> = xlPatternGrid\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PatternThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent1\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 Sheet1 中 C3 单元格中图案主题颜色是否为 xlThemeColorLight1。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PatternThemeColor</span> == xlThemeColorLight1)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "PatternTintAndShade",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置 <strong>Interior</strong> 对象的淡色和底纹图案。可读/写 <strong>Variant</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例对 Sheet1 中 A1:E4 区域单元格添加十字线图案，并将图案主题颜色设置为40%深色 xlThemeColorAccent4。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:E4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pattern</span> = xlPatternCrissCross\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PatternThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent4\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PatternTintAndShade</span> = -<span class=\"hljs-number\">0.4</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例对活动工作表中 B3:C4 区域单元格添加棋盘图案，并将图案主题颜色设置为60%浅色 xlThemeColorAccent2*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B3:C4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pattern</span> = xlPatternChecker\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PatternThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent2\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PatternTintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.6</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
