    {
      "name": "ThemeColor",
      "summary": "<p>如果对象当前未应用主题颜色，试图访问其主题颜色则会引起无效请求运行时错误。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置已应用的配色方案中的主题颜色，该配色方案与指定对象相关联。可读/写 <strong>Variant</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例对活动工作表 A1:D2 区域单元格添加网格图案，并将图案主题颜色设置为 xlThemeColorAccent4，单元格背景主题颜色设置为 xlThemeColorAccent2。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:D2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Pattern</span> = xlPatternGrid\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PatternThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent4\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent2\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表 A1:C2 区域背景主题颜色是否为 xlThemeColorDark2。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:C2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> == xlThemeColorDark2)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "TintAndShade",
      "summary": "<p>可以为 <strong>TintAndShade</strong> 属性输入 -1（最暗）到 1（最亮）之间的数字，零 (0) 为中间值。</p>\n<p>如果将此属性设置为小于 -1 或大于 1 的值，则会引起运行时错误：“指定的值超出了范围”。此属性用于主题颜色和非主题颜色。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Single</strong>，使颜色变深或变浅。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表 A1:B5 区域单元格内部设置为红色，并将亮度设置为0.5。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> interior = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:B5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>\n    interior.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 Sheet1 中 A4 单元格内部背景的亮度值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
